## Implementation Plan

* [ ] Add new GraphQL query

In order to fetch boards and lists like the REST query, we need to be able to fetch a single list under an issue board.

Example query to test:

```graphql
query {
  group(fullPath: "group") {
    board(id: "gid://gitlab/Board/3") {
      name
      list(id: "gid://gitlab/List/8") {
        id
        title
      }
    }
  }
}
```
